				<p>Giovani &#8212; Good catch. It should be softened a bit. I&#8217;ll edit that in.</p>
<p>Re, substituting honey for molasses &#8212; I&#8217;ve often done this in cakes but I haven&#8217;t tried it here. It <i>seems</i> like it would work but I can&#8217;t green light it without hearing that someone was successful in doing so. So, if you try it with a whole or partial honey swap, please report back. I am sure there are others either unable to get molasses or a little freaked out by its intensity.</p>
